{
  "number": 5527,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/5527",
  "title": "fix(insights): user-defined send/bindEvent overrides internal click",
  "body": "in sendEvent, we mark internal events (click and conversion), and prevent them being sent if there was a custom click right before. We also move bindEvent so that it happens _before_ sendEvent\r\n\r\nThis prevents automatic click when:\r\n- there's a bindEvent child\r\n- there's a sendEvent click before\r\n\r\nThis doesn't prevent when:\r\n- there's a sendEvent convert before\r\n- there's a view before\r\n- there's two internal clicks in a row\r\n\r\nFX-2246",
